name: GalaxyBUSD
description: GALAXY is a deflationary reflection token on the Binance Smart Chain. Holders receive 8% of all Buy & Sell transactions in Binance-Peg BUSD. 2% Transfer fee allows holders to move their tokens without the same Buy/Sell tax. GALAXY will be the utility token of an upcoming Decentralized Launchpad for new projects on Binance Smart Chain, PulseChain, and Safemoon Blockchain. Audit & KYC by InterFi Network.
